    <div style=\"background: #edf2f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0;\">
        <h3>ğŸ® Interactive Examples: Functions in Action!</h3>
        <pre style=\"background: #2d3748; color: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; overflow-x: auto;\"><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
