    &lt;h1 style=\"color: white; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\"&gt;ğŸ“ JavaScript Note Taker ğŸ“&lt;/h1&gt;
    
    &lt;div class=\"app-container\"&gt;
        &lt;h2&gt;Create Notes Dynamically!&lt;/h2&gt;
        
        &lt;div class=\"controls\"&gt;
