                "html": `<h1>Month 10, Week 38: Media Queries - The Transformer</h1>
<p>Today we learn how to make websites change their appearance automatically based on screen size - like a mood ring that changes color!</p>

<div class="analogy-box">
    <b>Analogy: The Mood Ring ğŸ“±â†’ğŸ’»</b><br/>
    A mood ring changes color based on temperature. A Media Query changes the website's design based on the <b>screen width</b>. When the screen is wide (desktop), it shows a horizontal menu. When it's narrow (phone), it transforms into a hamburger menu!
