<h3>What are Media Queries?</h3>
<div style="background-color: #f0f8ff; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 10px;">
    <h4>ğŸ“±ğŸ“Š Screen Size Breakpoints</h4>
    <p>Media queries let us apply CSS rules only when certain conditions are met (like screen width).</p>
    
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 15px 0;">
