    <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #fff3cd; border-radius: 5px;">
        <h5>ğŸ¯ Mobile-First vs Desktop-First Approach</h5>
        <p><b>Mobile-First (Recommended):</b> Start with mobile styles, then add media queries for larger screens</p>
        <p><b>Desktop-First:</b> Start with desktop styles, then adjust for smaller screens</p>
